## Comandos comunes

```bash
# Desarrollo
pnpm dev               # arranca Next.js en local

# Tests
pnpm test              # vitest watch
pnpm test --run        # vitest single run
pnpm test:e2e          # playwright

# Calidad
pnpm lint              # eslint
pnpm typecheck         # tsc --noEmit
pnpm format            # prettier

# Supabase local
pnpm supabase:start    # docker compose up
pnpm supabase:reset    # reset DB con migraciones
pnpm supabase:migrate  # nueva migracion

# Build
pnpm build             # next build
pnpm start             # next start (produccion local)
```

